{"tid":1697870,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有興趣一齊救動物？","createTime":"2019-11-07T06:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:39:52.000Z","uid":777,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b9695f338d2d8fc16aaf7619b0513ec0c7d1670f","tid":1697870,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n見到貓義工個中伏post<br />\n發覺真係好多人有不愉快經歷<br />\n包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺post個reply都有講<br />\n就係因為呢啲不愉快經歷我自己就做咗暫托<br />\n希望可以擋左一層異工<br />\n自己做多少少 幫到貓貓搵新屋企之餘<br />\n亦都幫到想養貓嘅人<br />\n<br />\n我reply完之後都多巴絲搵我<br />\n咁我自己一個接啲貓貓嚟托<br />\n進度其實好慢大家都要等好耐<br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗如果多啲人一齊做<br />\n咁就多啲貓受到幫助<br />\n其他巴絲又可以有貓貓陪<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇巴絲有咁嘅心可以一齊做呢啲事<br />\n包括暫托啦 捉貓捉狗啦 （如果可以夠人嘅話真係唔想淨係貓可以幫埋狗）<br />\n你有地方冇skill我可以教你 有心就得！<br />\n有錢買物資嘅又得 有力搬野又得<br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣嘅不如tg傾傾<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fkyouhk_gov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffkyouhk_gov&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=7afdf910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fkyouhk_gov</a><br />\n<br />\n社會氣氛唔好，返到家有貓狗相伴都係一種對心靈上嘅安慰。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命！"},{"pid":"802c36dc01efb3b421ae7c1c3ae8a7a643af73ca","tid":1697870,"uid":24671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"7802427b2d032f99da947925a8505fdd94c6957a","tid":1697870,"uid":200596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"Lm 未做過 冇skills但想幫手"},{"pid":"3e77d927c9d5538ccc44ce5168ed784399ca2f25","tid":1697870,"uid":777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7802427b2d032f99da947925a8505fdd94c6957a","tid":1697870,"uid":200596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"Lm 未做過 冇skills但想幫手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:37:42.000Z","msg":"tg針針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgm